# Production notes:
# - Use a PostgreSQL URL from Neon, Supabase, Vercel Postgres, or another managed Postgres provider.
# - If you switch Prisma from SQLite to PostgreSQL, update prisma/schema.prisma provider to "postgresql" before migration.
# - Add auth later with Clerk, Supabase Auth, or NextAuth at the dashboard layout boundary.
